reviewText: My boyfriend owns many issues of Playboy magazine back to August 1956 and a copy of the first issue that was sold December 1953. He made a list of the Asian Playmates in them. I think there have been 23. He corresponds with Lam Mei-Ling the June 2011 Playmate. He showed me issues with Chinese Playmates China Lee Miss August 1964, Diana Lee Miss May 1988 and Mei-Ling Lam Miss June 2011. She is his friend on Facebook and Twitter, and I have contacted her on Twitter as well. He has had over 100 Playboy videos. I see Diana Lee briefly in some of them. He has some Playmate Profile videos, and I wondered if Diana Lee was on one. I did a search and found two copies at Amazon, so I ordered one and received it so quickly I was amazed. I greatly enjoyed seeing Diana Lee in a long scene. She and I are Chinese, so she is one of my idols. She is beautiful and has a great figure. She is 5'-7", 118 pounds, while I am 5'-5", 102 pounds.
Miss May looking Great/ Lynn Thomas, Shae Marks, Carrie Jean Yazel, Diana Lee/ Playboy greats from the past are looking great in this VHS Video.
